headline: CVS Health Reports Earnings Thursday. The Stock Is Hot.
summary: CVS Health  is the hottest healthcare stock in the  gaining nearly 50% so far this year.  The massive health conglomerate, which holds a major insurer, a big retail pharmacy chain, and one of the largest U.S. pharmacy benefit managers, reports its first-quarter results on Thursday morning.  The results arrive as the company rides a wave of optimism.
